# PM Work Classification Rules

**Purpose**: Simple rules for when to create Tasks vs. track in session only
**Integration**: Works with existing Epic/Story/Task system without breaking it

## ðŸŽ¯ **CLASSIFICATION RULES**

### **When to Create Full Task:**
- Work estimated > 1 hour
- Work spans multiple sessions  
- Work requires stakeholder input/approval
- Work has dependencies or blocks other work
- Work generates important deliverables

### **When to Track in Session Only:**
- Work estimated < 1 hour
- Single session completion
- Simple updates, fixes, clarifications
- Administrative tasks

